<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head><%- include('partials/head', { title: title }) %></head>
<body class="public">
  <main class="wrap">
    <div class="home-hero">
      <div class="home-eyebrow">For pop-up artists</div>
      <h1 style="margin-top:12px;">Your pop-up,<br/><span class="brand"><span class="accent">live.</span></span></h1>
      <p class="lede">One beautiful link for your permanent-jewelry table, lash bar, or flash day — with a walk-in list your customers actually enjoy.</p>
      <form method="post" action="/create" style="margin-top:22px;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg btn-block" type="submit">Create my pop-up page — free</button>
      </form>
      <p class="small faint" style="margin-top:10px;">No sign-up. You get a private dashboard link instantly.</p>
    </div>

    <section class="card stack">
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="ico">🔗</div>
        <div><h3>A page you're proud to share</h3><p>Drop it in your IG bio and story. Warm, boutique, made for a phone — not a clunky booking form.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="ico">📝</div>
        <div><h3>A walk-in list that just works</h3><p>Customers scan the QR at your table and join. They watch their place in line; you tap “notify” when they’re up.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="feature">
        <div class="ico">✨</div>
        <div><h3>Every walk-in sees your work</h3><p>Your prices, your vibe, your Instagram — right where a new customer is already looking.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="card card-flat" style="margin-top:18px; background:var(--paper-2);">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin-top:0;">How the day goes</div>
      <ol class="muted" style="margin:0; padding-left:20px; line-height:1.9;">
        <li>Make your page &amp; add your chain menu.</li>
        <li>Create today’s pop-up, print or show the QR.</li>
        <li>Walk-ins scan, join the list, and browse while they wait.</li>
        <li>You notify &amp; serve — the line runs itself.</li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <p class="footer-mini">
      <span class="brand">Poppin<span class="accent">.</span></span> — a Gaime1 studio prototype. Free tier shown; a Pro plan (remove the footer, claim your handle, real SMS, deposits) is where it would pay.
    </p>
  </main>
  <script src="/static/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
